title: Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5
text:
> Texas Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5 Members of the Toronto Blue Jays celebrate following a three-run home run by teammate Jose Bautista during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto.
